\int \frac{2x dx}{\sqrt{1+x^2}}=(x^2+1)\frac{1}{\sqrt{1+x^2}}+\int(x^2+1)\frac{x}{(x^2+1)^{\frac{3}{2}}}dx
\int \frac{2x dx}{\sqrt{1+x^2}}=\sqrt{x^2+1}+\frac{1}{2}\int \frac{2x dx}{\sqrt{1+x^2}}
